WAS THE SAME SHARK
THAT I WAS USING?

19:16.503 --> 19:18.113
-ALL I KNOW IS THAT YOUR
CAREER IS DANGLING BY A THREAD,

19:18.244 --> 19:20.159
AS A DIRECTOR AND A LIFEGUARD.

19:26.165 --> 19:28.254
-I KNOW YOU'RE ALL AWARE
OF THE SHARK STORIES

19:28.384 --> 19:30.169
FLOATING AROUND HEADQUARTERS,
BUT AT THIS TIME WE HAVE

19:30.299 --> 19:32.606
NO DEFINITIVE PROOF THAT ANYONE
HAS ACTUALLY BEEN ATTACKED.

19:32.736 --> 19:34.260
-SO, LET'S NOT LOSE FOCUS

19:34.390 --> 19:37.001
ON THE EVERYDAY ASPECTS
OF THE JOB, OKAY?

19:37.132 --> 19:38.655
ALL RIGHT, HAVE A GOOD
ONE AND WATCH YOUR FEET,

19:38.786 --> 19:40.744
THERE'S A LOT OF
STINGRAYS OUT THERE.

19:40.875 --> 19:42.311
YOU, KEEP YOUR
EYES ON THE WATER.

19:42.442 --> 19:43.704
-I WILL, THANKS, MITCH.

19:43.834 --> 19:44.879
-DID YOU STOP WORKING
OUT COMPLETELY?

19:46.315 --> 19:47.925
NEWMIE, WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

19:48.056 --> 19:48.926
I THOUGHT YOU WERE STILL
WORKING ON LOGAN'S MOVIE?

19:49.057 --> 19:49.840
-GOT LAID OFF.

19:49.971 --> 19:50.798
-AWW.

19:50.928 --> 19:52.321
-YEAH, HE'S TAPPED OUT,

19:52.452 --> 19:53.409
THEY'RE GONNA BE
SHUTTING DOWN PRODUCTION.

19:53.540 --> 19:54.671
-WELL, THAT'S SHOW BIZ, MAN.

19:54.802 --> 19:55.977
ANYTHING I CAN DO TO HELP?

19:56.107 --> 19:57.021
-ANYONE WORKING GIDGEE GULCH?

19:57.152 --> 19:57.935
-YOU ARE.

19:58.066 --> 19:58.980
-YEAH, THANKS.

19:59.937 --> 20:01.461
-I THOUGHT WE HAD AN AGREEMENT,

20:01.591 --> 20:03.419
YOU'VE STILL GOT ANTHONY
AND DONNA SHARING A TOWER.

20:03.550 --> 20:05.465
-OH MY GOD, I THOUGHT
I MADE THAT CHANGE.

20:05.595 --> 20:07.075
-NO, YOU DIDN'T.

20:07.206 --> 20:08.772
-WELL I WAS GONNA PUT
HER WITH SOMEONE ELSE.

20:08.903 --> 20:11.297
-LIKE NEWMIE, NEWMIE
WOULD BE PERFECT.

20:11.427 --> 20:13.647
NOW HE COULD TEACH HER A THING
OR TWO ABOUT LIFEGUARDING.

20:13.777 --> 20:15.039
-SO COULD YOU.
-WHAT?

20:15.170 --> 20:16.563
-TOWER 12 WITH DONNA.

20:17.085 --> 20:18.434
-MITCH, DON'T DO THIS TO ME.

20:18.565 --> 20:19.957
-OH, IT'LL BE GOOD FOR YOU.

20:20.088 --> 20:21.045
YOU KNOW, KINDA TAKE
HER UNDER YOUR WING.

20:22.438 --> 20:23.526
-MITCH, MITCH.

20:23.657 --> 20:24.919
-YEAH, WHAT'S UP?

20:25.049 --> 20:26.355
-JUST GOT THE RESULTS
BACK FROM UCLA.

20:27.095 --> 20:29.576
THEY MEASURED THE BITE
RADIUS AND GUESS WHAT?

20:29.706 --> 20:30.838
LOGAN'S OFF THE HOOK.

20:31.491 --> 20:33.667
WASN'T A TIGER SHARK
THAT ATE MY BOARD,

20:34.407 --> 20:35.843
IT WAS A GREAT WHITE.

20:41.544 --> 20:46.549
-[ROCK MUSIC]

21:52.354 --> 21:57.707
[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

22:20.904 --> 22:22.602
-CUT, CUT, CUT!

22:22.732 --> 22:23.777
-DID YOU GET IT?

22:23.907 --> 22:24.778
-THAT WAS GREAT.

22:24.908 --> 22:27.868
-OKAY, PRINT THAT ONE.

22:27.998 --> 22:29.783
THAT'S TEN MINUTES
FOR LUNCH EVERYBODY.

22:31.567 --> 22:34.831
-NOT WHILE WE'VE GOT THE LIGHT,
LET'S MOVE ON TO SCENE 16.

22:39.314 --> 22:40.228
-DID YOU GET IT?

22:40.359 --> 22:41.795
-YEAH, I GOT IT.

22:41.925 --> 22:45.059
SO, WAS THAT YOUR
ALFRED HITCHCOCK CAMEO?

22:46.321 --> 22:48.192
-NO I CAN'T AFFORD TO
PAY MORE CAST CALLS.

22:48.323 --> 22:49.890
-YEAH, SPEAKING OF GETTING PAID.

22:50.934 --> 22:52.283
-UH OH.

22:52.414 --> 22:53.981
-[SIRENS]

22:54.111 --> 22:55.722
-LOOKS LIKE A BUST.

23:04.557 --> 23:05.688
-HEY, WHAT'S GOING ON?

23:05.819 --> 23:07.081
-WE'RE SHUTTING YOU DOWN.

23:07.211 --> 23:08.561
-SHUTTING US DOWN?

23:08.691 --> 23:10.171
WHAT'D THEY SAY AT UCLA?

23:10.301 --> 23:12.216
-IT WASN'T A TIGER
SHARK THAT ATTACKED CODY.

23:12.347 --> 23:13.348
-I KNEW IT.

23:13.479 --> 23:14.697
-IT WAS A GREAT WHITE.

23:15.872 --> 23:17.570
-A GREAT WHITE?

23:17.700 --> 23:19.441
-I WANT EVERYBODY OUT OF THE
WATER INCLUDING YOUR CAST.

23:20.224 --> 23:21.574
-WHAT'S LEFT OF IT.

23:21.704 --> 23:23.314
-MITCH: I WANT YOU
OUT OF THE AREA, LOGAN.

23:23.445 --> 23:24.838
-MITCH, IF THERE'S A
GREAT WHITE OUT THERE

23:24.968 --> 23:26.143
I HAVE TO FILM IT.

23:26.274 --> 23:27.797
I MAY NEVER GET
THIS CHANCE AGAIN.

23:27.928 --> 23:29.756
-YOU ENDANGER
ONE PERSON'S LIFE,

23:29.886 --> 23:32.715
YOU'LL BE FLIPPING
HAMBURGERS BACK IN TASMANIA.

23:36.197 --> 23:37.328
-WE'LL SEE.

23:39.287 --> 23:40.288
WE'LL SEE.

23:40.897 --> 23:42.029
GET READY.

23:50.733 --> 23:56.391
