26:44.994 --> 26:47.040
-I BET LOGAN IS LOVING ALL THIS

26:47.170 --> 26:48.911
FREE PUBLICITY FOR HIS MOVIE.

26:50.130 --> 26:51.348
-IF I DIDN'T KNOW
