-I READ THE SCRIPT,
IT WASN'T HALF BAD.

26:58.486 --> 27:00.662
-I KNOW, I HATE TO ADMIT IT.
HE'S PRETTY TALENTED.

27:01.489 --> 27:02.882
MORE TALENTED THAN HE DESERVES.

27:03.578 --> 27:07.147
-SO WHAT, IS THIS THE END OF
YOUR GLORIOUS ACTING CAREER?

27:07.974 --> 27:09.758
-I THINK I'LL STICK TO
LIFEGUARDING FOR NOW.

27:10.629 --> 27:12.239
BUT WHO KNOWS, DOWN THE LINE

27:12.369 --> 27:13.936
I MIGHT GIVE IT ANOTHER WHIRL.

27:14.545 --> 27:16.504
KINDA LIKED BEING IN
FRONT OF THAT CAMERA.

27:29.517 --> 27:31.388
-LIFEGUARD! LIFEGUARD!

27:31.519 --> 27:32.781
I CAN'T FIND MY DAUGHTER!

27:32.912 --> 27:34.653
-OKAY, WHAT DOES SHE LOOK LIKE?

27:34.783 --> 27:36.916
-SHE'S SIX YEARS OLD, SHE
HAS BLONDE HAIR AND BLUE EYES.

27:37.046 --> 27:38.831
LISA!

27:40.571 --> 27:42.617
LISA!

27:43.966 --> 27:46.708
OH MY GOD, THAT'S HER BUCKET.

27:46.839 --> 27:49.145
OH, LISA!

27:49.276 --> 27:51.060
-MA'AM, PLEASE DON'T GO IN.

27:51.191 --> 27:52.148
-LISA: MOMMY.

27:55.891 --> 27:58.938
-OH, LISA, WHERE DID YOU GO?

27:59.068 --> 28:00.635
YOU HAD ME WORRIED TO DEATH.

28:00.766 --> 28:02.158
-SHE WAS CHASING A SAND CRAB

28:02.289 --> 28:03.986
AND I THINK SHE LOST
TRACK OF WHERE SHE WAS.

28:04.117 --> 28:05.074
-THANK YOU SO MUCH.

28:05.205 --> 28:06.728
-OH, IT'S MY PLEASURE.

28:12.734 --> 28:14.170
-THANKS A LOT, SHE WAS STARTING

28:14.301 --> 28:15.694
TO GET A LITTLE FREAKED OUT.

28:15.824 --> 28:17.565
-SO WAS I, WHEN I
SAW YOU TALKING TO HER

28:17.696 --> 28:19.436
WITH YOUR BACK TO THE WATER.

28:19.567 --> 28:21.351
WHAT'S THE FIRST THING THEY
TAUGHT YOU IN ROOKIE SCHOOL?

28:21.482 --> 28:23.179
YOUR EYES NEVER LEAVE THE WATER.

28:23.310 --> 28:25.181
-I WAS TRYING TO KEEP
HER FROM GOING IN.

28:25.921 --> 28:27.357
-LOOK, I KNOW YOU'RE GONNA BE

28:27.488 --> 28:28.881
AN EXCELLENT LIFEGUARD SOMEDAY,

28:29.577 --> 28:31.013
BUT YOU STILL GOT
A LOT TO LEARN.

28:31.797 --> 28:32.711
-NEELY!

28:33.799 --> 28:35.844
LOOK, I DON'T WANNA GET
OFF ON THE WRONG FOOT.

28:35.975 --> 28:38.499
SO LET'S GET SOMETHING
STRAIGHT BETWEEN US RIGHT NOW,

28:38.629 --> 28:41.545
I KNOW ABOUT YOU AND ANTHONY,
AND I WANT YOU TO KNOW

28:41.676 --> 28:45.245
-I'M NOT INTERESTED IN HIM,
NEVER WAS, NEVER WILL BE.

28:46.333 --> 28:49.249
I DON'T BELIEVE IN STEALING
A CO-WORKERS BOYFRIEND,

28:49.379 --> 28:52.252
NOR DO I INTEND TO GET INVOLVED
WITH ANYONE AT BAYWATCH.

28:52.382 --> 28:54.515
I HAVE A STRICT POLICY AGAINST

28:54.645 --> 28:56.082
MIXING BUSINESS WITH PLEASURE.

28:56.604 --> 28:58.127
ARE WE CLEAR ON THAT?

28:58.693 --> 29:01.435
-CRYSTAL CLEAR.
-DONNA: GOOD.

29:05.482 --> 29:07.049
-WOMAN: HEY, LET'S GO.

29:12.011 --> 29:16.885
-[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

29:22.412 --> 29:24.284
-NEELY: ALWAYS A
COUPLE OF WISE GUYS.

29:24.414 --> 29:25.807
THE BEACH IS CLOSED!

29:29.419 --> 29:30.638
HEY, GET BACK IN HERE!

29:30.769 --> 29:32.292
CAN'T YOU READ THE SIGN?

29:34.685 --> 29:36.687
LOOKS LIKE WE'RE GONNA
HAVE TO GO GET 'EM.

29:49.526 --> 29:51.615
WE'RE NOT JOKING, BOYS.
THERE'S A SHARK ALERT

29:51.746 --> 29:54.488
AT ALL MALIBU BEACHES,
GET OUT OF THE WATER NOW.

29:55.794 --> 30:00.973
-[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

30:07.414 --> 30:10.460
I'LL GET THAT BUNCH, YOU
GET THE LITTLE HOT DOG.

30:14.725 --> 30:17.206
YOU GUYS, SHARK
ALERT. COME ON, GET IN.

30:26.999 --> 30:28.478
-OH GOD!

30:41.970 --> 30:45.582
-SHARK! SHARK!
-[SCREAMS]

31:20.574 --> 31:21.575
-HELP!

31:21.705 --> 31:22.881
-DONNA: GRAB THE CAN.

31:24.056 --> 31:25.666
IT'S ALL RIGHT.

31:25.796 --> 31:27.320
DO YOU KNOW HOW LUCKY YOU ARE?

31:35.676 --> 31:37.504
-RADIO: WE HAVE ANOTHER
CONFIRMED SHARK ATTACK

31:37.634 --> 31:40.072
OFF TOWER 15, CLEAR THE
WATER OF ALL SWIMMERS.

31:40.202 --> 31:41.595
-WE'VE GOT A COUPLE
SURFERS WITH SPEAR GUNS

31:41.725 --> 31:43.902
HEADED TOWARDS THE AREA,
COVER MY WATER WILL YA?

31:47.862 --> 31:49.081
LET'S GO!

31:52.345 --> 31:54.173
-RADIO: NINE FIVE TO
ALL AVAILABLE UNITS,

31:54.303 --> 31:56.088
RESPOND CODE THREE TO MALIBU
12, CONFIRMED SHARK ATTACK.

31:56.218 --> 31:57.872
-OKAY PEOPLE, THIS COULD BE IT.

31:59.569 --> 32:04.531
-[ROCK MUSIC]

32:08.143 --> 32:09.231
-HANG ON.

32:18.458 --> 32:19.372
-FULL THROTTLE.

32:33.864 --> 32:34.909
-GET OUT OF THE WATER.

32:35.040 --> 32:36.693
-WE AIN'T AFRAID OF NO SHARK.

32:36.824 --> 32:38.957
-OH, COME ON, ALL RIGHT,
WE KNOW HOW MACHO YOU ARE,

32:39.087 --> 32:40.045
YOU'VE PROVEN YOUR POINT.

32:40.175 --> 32:41.568
NOW START PADDLING, OKAY?

32:42.090 --> 32:43.700
-UNLESS YOU WANT
US TO DRAG YOU IN.

32:43.831 --> 32:45.572
-ALL RIGHT, ALL RIGHT.

32:52.883 --> 32:54.842
-UGH LOOK, IT'S LOGAN.

32:56.148 --> 32:57.932
-THIS IS GREAT, AS IF WE
DIDN'T HAVE ENOUGH PROBLEMS.

32:58.063 --> 32:59.629
YOU KNOW I BET YOU ANYTHING

32:59.760 --> 33:00.979
THAT HE WAS MONITORING
THE LIFEGUARD FREQUENCIES.

33:01.109 --> 33:05.157
-[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

33:06.332 --> 33:07.681
-[THUMP]

33:08.551 --> 33:09.683
WHAT WAS THAT?

33:09.813 --> 33:11.032
-GET AS CLOSE AS YOU CAN.

33:11.163 --> 33:12.425
-YUP.

33:22.217 --> 33:24.872
-[SCREAMING]

33:29.746 --> 33:31.661
-DAMN, I JUST RAN OUT OF FILM.

33:31.792 --> 33:33.272
-WHAT DO YOU MEAN YOU
JUST RAN OUT OF FILM?

33:33.402 --> 33:34.751
-RELOAD!
-HURRY!

33:44.718 --> 33:45.936
-MITCH!

33:46.067 --> 33:46.894
SHARK!

33:47.025 --> 33:49.201
[SCREAMING]

33:54.641 --> 33:57.122
-KEEP ROLLING, STAY WITH HIM.

33:58.253 --> 33:59.428
-CAROLINE: HELP!

33:59.559 --> 34:01.039
-COME ON!

34:08.655 --> 34:10.091
COME ON.

34:17.228 --> 34:19.969
-[SCREAMING]

34:21.536 --> 34:22.886
-COME ON, MITCH!

34:24.757 --> 34:26.020
SWIM!

34:26.585 --> 34:27.848
COME ON!

34:28.891 --> 34:30.155
HE'S RIGHT BEHIND YOU.

34:32.199 --> 34:33.549
SWIM!

34:35.333 --> 34:39.206
-[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

35:01.316 --> 35:02.926
-WHAT AN INCREDIBLE SPECIMEN.

35:19.117 --> 35:20.205
TIME TO RELIVE YOUR
NAVY SEAL DAYS.

35:20.335 --> 35:21.293
-WHAT?

35:21.423 --> 35:22.294
-HERE, TIE THIS TO THE LINE.

35:22.424 --> 35:23.817
-WHAT? WHAT FOR?

35:23.947 --> 35:25.949
-TRACKING, REMEMBER THE
YELLOW BARRELS IN JAWS?

35:26.080 --> 35:27.647
-SHARK ON THE STARBOARD SIDE.

35:27.777 --> 35:29.344
-THIS IS THE LIFEGUARD VERSION.

35:31.781 --> 35:35.307
-[DRAMATIC MUSIC]

35:41.313 --> 35:42.357
-HARD LEFT!

35:44.316 --> 35:45.708
-WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

35:45.839 --> 35:47.188
-TELL HIM TO STAND
STILL, I CAN'T FOCUS.

35:47.319 --> 35:48.972
-READY.
-WAIT, HE'S NOT IN FRAME.

35:49.103 --> 35:50.452
-IT'S NOT A MOVIE, LOGAN.

35:50.583 --> 35:52.019
-NOW!
-LOGAN: ACTION!

36:04.249 --> 36:05.467
-MITCH: GOT IT.

36:05.598 --> 36:07.339
-CAROLINE: GOOD SHOT MITCH.

36:10.429 --> 36:11.604
-LOGAN: KEEP ROLLING.

36:12.561 --> 36:14.650
-I'M RUNNING OUT OF FILM,
I BETTER RELOAD NOW.

36:20.830 --> 36:22.441
-ALL RIGHT, LET'S GET
THE HELL OUT OF HERE.

36:22.571 --> 36:23.964
GET ME THE COAST GUARD
ON THE HORN.

36:24.094 --> 36:25.226
-I DON'T THINK SO.

36:26.358 --> 36:27.620
-WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

36:27.750 --> 36:29.187
-THIS IS A PRIVATELY
OWNED VESSEL,

36:29.317 --> 36:30.884
YOU HAVE NO RIGHT TO
COMMANDEER THIS BOAT.

36:31.014 --> 36:32.581
-LOGAN, YOU WANT
THIS FILM OR NOT?

36:32.712 --> 36:33.582
-YUP.

36:37.456 --> 36:39.719
-[YELLING]

36:47.727 --> 36:48.728
-MITCH: LOGAN!

36:48.858 --> 36:50.164
GET THE HELL OUT OF THE WATER!

36:50.295 --> 36:51.165
COME ON MAN!

36:51.296 --> 36:52.384
LOGAN, COME ON.

36:52.514 --> 36:55.082
COME ON, GET THE CAN!

36:57.084 --> 36:58.564
HE'S RIGHT BEHIND YOU.

36:58.694 --> 37:00.914
COME ON LOGAN! COME ON!

37:02.394 --> 37:05.527
-[SHOUTING]

37:08.617 --> 37:09.705
-COME ON!

37:19.802 --> 37:21.282
COME ON LOGAN!

37:22.327 --> 37:23.458
COME ON!

37:25.330 --> 37:26.983
HE'S RIGHT BEHIND YOU!

37:36.689 --> 37:38.821
WAKE UP, COME ON, LOGAN.

38:12.072 --> 38:12.855
NICE WORK.

38:12.986 --> 38:14.422
-THANKS.

38:14.553 --> 38:17.077
-I'LL SAY, HOW'D YOU
FIGURE THAT OUT SO FAST?

38:17.207 --> 38:19.471
THE GAS CAN, THE CHUM
BUCKET, THE FLARE GUN,

38:19.601 --> 38:20.776
THAT WAS PURE GENIUS.

38:20.907 --> 38:22.822
-OH NOT REALLY, THAT'S HOW

38:22.952 --> 38:25.085
THEY KILLED THE SHARK
IN JAWS: THE REVENGE.

38:25.215 --> 38:27.261
-GEEZ, YOU GUYS
STEAL EVERYTHING.

38:30.786 --> 38:32.701
-MITCH: LOGAN,
GIVE IT UP ALREADY.

38:33.833 --> 38:34.790
-YES!

38:39.708 --> 38:40.579
NO!

38:47.890 --> 38:52.895
-[ROCK MUSIC]

38:59.685 --> 39:02.514
-MAKE SURE YOU CHECK THE RIPS
AT ZUMA, THEY'RE PRETTY BAD.

39:03.602 --> 39:04.472
-HEY MITCH.

39:06.561 --> 39:07.562
-LOGAN.

39:08.737 --> 39:10.609
-UM, I WAS WONDERING
IF YOU COULD SIGN THIS.

39:10.739 --> 39:11.871
-WHAT IS IT?

39:12.437 --> 39:13.742
-IT'S A WAIVER SO I
CAN USE THE FOOTAGE

39:13.873 --> 39:15.091
THAT WAS SHOT OF YOU.

39:15.222 --> 39:16.919
YOU'LL BE FULLY
COMPENSATED, OF COURSE.

39:18.399 --> 39:20.488
-I THOUGHT THE FILM
WAS LOST AT SEA.

39:21.446 --> 39:22.925
-WELL ACTUALLY WE
SHOT SEVERAL REELS

39:23.056 --> 39:24.666
AND I'VE BEEN IN THE
EDITING ROOM ALL MORNING.

39:25.493 --> 39:27.365
THERE'S SOME INCREDIBLE
STUFF THERE, YOU KNOW?

39:32.065 --> 39:33.283
-WHAT IF I DON'T SIGN?

39:34.372 --> 39:37.026
-LOOK, I KNOW I GOT OUT
OF CONTROL ON THE BOAT,

39:38.680 --> 39:40.595
I JUST GOT CARRIED AWAY.

39:41.466 --> 39:42.902
-LITTLE LATE FOR APOLOGIES, PAL.

39:44.077 --> 39:46.296
-THEN HOW WOULD YOU FEEL IF
I OFFERED YOU MY RESIGNATION?

39:48.647 --> 39:50.997
LOOK, I COMPROMISED MY
RELATIONSHIP WITH YOU

39:51.127 --> 39:52.607
AND MY DUTIES AS A LIFEGUARD.

39:53.869 --> 39:55.436
I VIOLATED YOUR TRUST.

39:56.611 --> 39:59.527
AND THIS TIME, I DON'T
THINK I CAN GET IT BACK.

40:01.442 --> 40:05.228
-LOGAN, YOU'VE BEEN
